<br>
However, there are a few exceptions to that, I guess.  Why don't NPC monks FD?  Why doesn't your common NPC Rogue try to evade?  And why, when that NPC ranger is chasing me, can I sprint across the zone and eventually get far enough to clear aggro?  Shouldn't he be able to track me down?<br>
